1 Mama agre vyaktatā pakṣau yasya
2 Sundaram rūpam yat sukha-anubhavena
3 Santuṣṭāḥ ātmānaḥ kṛtvā saṅgamam kurvanti;

7 Yat tu mama smaraṇīyamasti,
8 tat kathañcana vācā na nītam, na lekhanīyānena likhitam,
9 na ca kathañcana kalpitatayāpi gṛhītam;

13 Eva ca ārabhata: "Dharmyo bhaktaścaiva
14 Aham atra samuddhṛtaḥ sāṃ jayoḥ
15 Yaḥ kāmayā na vijityaḥ;

46 Evaṃ ca niścitam yad ādi-garvī,
47 yaḥ āsīt sarva-prakṛter utkarṣaḥ,
48 prakāśam anāpekṣya patitaḥ āsīt tīkṣṇaḥ;

58 Tathāpi nitye nyāye
59 dṛṣṭiḥ yāṃ gṛhṇāti bhavataḥ lokaḥ,
60 yathā cakṣuḥ samudre, antraḥ praviśati;

67 Ati te mokṣaḥ prakāśitaḥ
68 yaḥ tvām nyavarṇayat jīvantam nyāyam,
69 yasya viṣaye tvam praśnam cakāraḥ punaḥ punaḥ;

70 yataḥ tvam uvācaḥ: “Ekaḥ puruṣaḥ jāyate nadītīre
71 Sindhu-nadyāḥ, tatra ca na asti yaḥ kathāpayati
72 Kṛṣṭasya viṣaye na vā yaḥ pathate na vā yaḥ likhati;

91 Yathā nidherupari paribhramata iti
92 tataḥ śiśūn paścāt paśyati valākā,
93 tathā ca te śiśavaḥ paśyanti tām;

106 Api paśya: bahvaḥ krandanti “Kṛṣṭaḥ, Kṛṣṭaḥ!”,
107 Ye nyāyādhikaraṇe bhaviṣyanti atiśayaṃ dūre
108 Tasya, yaḥ Kṛṣṭaṃ na jānāti;
